==English==
===Etymology===
From the Latin ''cithara'', from the Greek ''kithara''

===Noun===
'''zither'''
{{wikipedia}}
# a [[musical instrument]] consisting of a flat sounding box with numerous strings, placed on a horizontal surface, and played with a [[plectrum]] and fingertips; similar to a [[dulcimer]].

